episodes.title: Conquest of Cuteness
episodes.plot: Finn and Jake come under attack in their home from a race of super-evil creatures which are too cute to be taken seriously.

episodes.title: Morituri Te Salutamus
episodes.plot: Finn and Jake end up in a haunted arena where they must fight ghost gladiators to escape.

episodes.title: Memory of a Memory
episodes.plot: Finding their friend, Marceline the Vampire Queen, in a deep sleep, a mysterious stranger helps Finn and Jake by sending them into her dreams to awaken her.

episodes.title: Hitman
episodes.plot: The Ice King looks to hire a professional bully to beat up Finn and Jake, but inadvertently hires a deadly, unstoppable contract killer.

episodes.title: Too Young
episodes.plot: Finn is happy that Princess Bubblegum has regressed to the same age as him. But soon a challenger for the throne arrives to unseat the newly underage princess.

episodes.title: The Monster
episodes.plot: The king and queen of Lumpy Space ask Finn to find and return Lumpy Space Princess, who has been living in the woods and mistaken as a monster.

episodes.title: Still
episodes.plot: The Ice King uses a potion that paralyzes Finn and Jake, who become the lonely villain's unwilling best friends.

episodes.title: Wizard Battle
episodes.plot: The Ice King enters a battle of wizards from all over the Land of Ooo, to win a kiss from Princess Bubblegum--which Finn and Jake look to prevent.

episodes.title: Fionna and Cake
episodes.plot: In a world where all the characters are different genders, the adventurer Fionna gets advice from her cat-friend Cake on her date with Prince Gumball.

episodes.title: What Was Missing
episodes.plot: In order to open a magic door filled with stolen items, Finn and all his friends must perform in a band. But everyone's differing musical tastes and overall tensions make things difficult.

episodes.title: Apple Thief
episodes.plot: After Tree Trunks finds her apples have gone missing, Finn and Jake search the criminal underworld of the Candy Kingdom to recover them.

episodes.title: The Creeps
episodes.plot: Finn's masquerade birthday party turns into a deadly mystery.

episodes.title: From Bad to Worse
episodes.plot: The undead plague returns to the Candy Kingdom.

episodes.title: Beautopia
episodes.plot: Susan Strong returns and asks Finn and Jake to save her people from the Glubs. But Finn is still not sure if he can trust her after last time.

episodes.title: No One Can Hear You
episodes.plot: After trying to stop a deer that has been licking the Candy Kingdom people, Finn wakes up in a hospital to find everyone missing except Jake who is acting very strange.

episodes.title: Jake vs. Me-Mow
episodes.plot: A tiny cat assassin tries to black mail Jake into killing someone, by hiding in his nose with some poison.

episodes.title: Thank You
episodes.plot: A fire-breathing wolf cub becomes lost in the snowy woods and becomes unlikely friends with a tall snow-creature.

episodes.title: The New Frontier
episodes.plot: Jake has a dream that seems to foretell his death but, to Finn's dismay, doesn't take it serious.

episodes.title: Holly Jolly Secrets
episodes.plot: In part two of the holiday special, The Ice King tries to get his video diary back from Finn and Jake.

episodes.title: Marceline's Closet
episodes.plot: Bored waiting for her, Finn and Jake sneak into Marceline's house, become trapped when she comes home, and witness her strange behavior when she's alone.

episodes.title: Paper Pete
episodes.plot: A secret war takes place in the library between tiny paper people and mold creatures, and Finn is brought into the middle of it all.

episodes.title: Another Way
episodes.plot: Finn journeys for a cyclops's magical tears to cure his injuries, but have trouble because of his stubborn inability to follow the advice of others.

episodes.title: Ghost Princess
episodes.plot: Finn and Jake try to help Ghost Princess by solving her murder.

episodes.title: Dad's Dungeon
episodes.plot: Finn and Jake discover a lost message from their dad which sends them to a mysterious and dangerous dungeon.

episodes.title: Incendium
episodes.plot: Trying to help Finn get over his hopeless feelings for Princess Bubblegum, Jake sets out to find a new princess for Finn to go out with.
